        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Safe School Drinking Water Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Environmental Protection Agency to establish a program to award grants to assist local educational agencies in installing and maintaining filtration stations (e.g., drinking fountains) at schools and child care programs.</p>]]>
        </text>
